 class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.Result\">Result</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"No change. If `done = true`, skip remaining simplification steps for this term. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.Result.rfl","kind":"ctor","line":38,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.Result.rfl","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.lean#L38-L39"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.Result\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">DSimp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Result</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The result of definitionally simplifying an expression `e`.\n\nThe `done` flag controls whether simplification should continue after this result:\n- `done = false` (default): Continue with subsequent simplification steps. If a\n  `pre`/`post` method returns `.step e' false`, `dsimp` recurses on `e'`.\n- `done = true`: Stop processing, return this result as final.\n\nUnlike `Sym.Simp.Result`, this carries no proof term and no `contextDependent` flag.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.Result","kind":"inductive","line":27,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.Result","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.lean#L27-L42"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.instInhabitedConfig\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">DSimp</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedConfig</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.Config\">Config</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.instInhabitedConfig","kind":"instance","line":25,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.instInhabitedConfig","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.lean#L25-L25"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.Config.maxSteps\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">DSimp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Config</span>.<span class=\"name\">maxSteps</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.Config\">Config</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Maximum number of steps that can be performed by the simplifier. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.Config.maxSteps","kind":"def","line":24,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.Config.maxSteps","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.lean#L24-L24"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lea